title: @OspreyWTEN Finishes Day One of Bedford Cup
text: fell in her first round match, 6-2, 2-6, 7-8 (7-2). In the Round of 16 for the Singles A bracket, Hemmerich, Valdez and Vazquez fell in their second round matches. In the Singles B bracket, Intert won her match 6-4, 6-1, while Calderon fell 6-4, 6-0. We also learned today that each one of us needs each other's support and tenacity when competing on the court. We were very good at showing support for teammates, however, we have to improve our openness to feeling and embracing this support," added Cohen. "I felt as though we internalized and individualized our feelings of doubt, and tomorrow I expect that we change this by embracing our teammate's and coach's positivity." The action continues tomorrow in the second day of play from Fort Myers.
